.printnum
/ *#toprint 1000

% r 10

out r 1
/ *#toprint 10
% r 10
+ 60 r
out r 1
% *#toprint 10

jmp *#returnto 1

.begin
set #num 1

.loop

set #num r
root 2 r

.chkfctr

>= *#root *#factor

set #returnto #pos
set #toprint *#num
jmp #printnum 1
.pos
halt
jmp #loop 1
.toosmall

% *#num *#factor
swtch #loop #chkfctr
